            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-07-22T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-10-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="71" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d71">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For texts of an address by President Truman before the Canadian Parliament in
                    Ottawa, June 11, and of a special news conference with Prime Minister Mackenzie
                    King near Ottawa, June 12, see <hi rend="italic">Public Papers of the Presidents
                        of the United States: Harry S. Truman, 1947</hi> (Washington, Government
                    Printing Office, 1963), pages 272–277.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
